sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: User Authentication and Frontend Access

    User->>Route: GET / (initial request)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward to OAuth Proxy
    OAuth->>OAuthServer: Redirect (no token)<br/>OAuth Client Secret
    OAuthServer->>User: Login page
    User->>OAuthServer: POST credentials
    OAuthServer->>User: Redirect with token (cookie)
    User->>Route: GET / with Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward with token<br/>TLS (service cert)
    OAuth->>Backend: GET / (localhost)<br/>HTTP with Bearer Token header
    Backend-->>OAuth: Frontend HTML/JS/CSS
    OAuth-->>User: Frontend application

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: API Request to Kubernetes

    User->>OAuth: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token (cookie)
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTP + Bearer Token header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>User Bearer Token (impersonation)<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR created
    Backend-->>OAuth: Response (JSON)
    OAuth-->>User: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Notebook Creation Workflow

    User->>OAuth: POST /api/notebooks create<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward request
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Check/Create Namespace<br/>User Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Namespace ready
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>User Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC (RoleBindings)<br/>User Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: RBAC created
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success response
    OAuth-->>User: Notebook created

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Query

    User->>OAuth: GET /api/prometheus?query=...<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward request
    Backend->>Prometheus: PromQL query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Prometheus-->>Backend: Metrics data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>User: Metrics visualization
